# Risk levels:
#   L0: auto_allow ŌĆö always permit
#   L1: auto_allow_session ŌĆö permit after first approval this session
#   L2: observer_evaluate ŌĆö post-hoc audit via rule engine
#   L3: halt ŌĆö unconditionally deny, halt pipeline, notify operator
