- Which fields to fill in (every `<USER MUST FILL>` marker).
- How to run `unison dry-run` to validate.
- How to run `unison run` to start the pipeline.

## Error Handling

| Scenario | Behavior |
|----------|----------|
| Source file missing | Migrator reports the missing file and generates a placeholder with a `<!-- MISSING SOURCE -->` comment |
| `target-demo/` already exists | Migrator overwrites template files but does not delete user-created files |
| YAML parse error in generated output | Migrator reports the error; dry-run fails |
| `<USER MUST FILL>` in required fields | Dry-run warns but does not error (user may have filled them in) |

